725689f-a.title: Queens: 85th Street - Astoria Boulevard
725689f-a.text:
85th Street, north from Astoria Boulevard, showing the thoroughfare shortly after it was constructed . All this land was formely the Kouwenhoven farm. The cottage shown in view
2 is at 24th Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  October 19, 1935
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
